      "content": "Analyzed MarkdownGenerator class in formatter.py (231 lines) and DocumentationGenerator integration in generator.py. \n\nCurrent Structure Analysis:\n\nMarkdownGenerator class (formatter.py:18-199):\n- Main entry: `generate()` method (line 25) - orchestrates all sections\n- Section generators (all private methods):\n  1. `_header()` (line 38) - Project name, version, timestamp\n  2. `_statistics()` (line 47) - Overall project stats\n  3. `_language_breakdown()` (line 65) - Multi-language stats\n  4. `_classes()` (line 87) - Class documentation\n  5. `_functions()` (line 131) - Function documentation\n  6. `_dependencies()` (line 183) - Dependency graph\n\nIntegration with generator.py:\n- DocumentationGenerator.generate() (line 79) - Creates analysis dict + statistics\n- generate_all() (line 264) - Calls generate(), then save_markdown()/save_json()\n- save_markdown() writes single file to output_dir/DOCUMENTATION.md\n- Currently monolithic: all sections joined with '\\n\\n' and written once\n\nShard Extraction Strategy:\n\nList of section generators to extract:\n1. index.md \u2192 New generator combining _header() + quick_reference + doc_links\n2. project-overview.md \u2192 Extract from enhanced _statistics() + new overview content\n3. architecture.md \u2192 New generator (will need AI consultation integration)\n4. source-tree-analysis.md \u2192 New generator using module data\n5. component-inventory.md \u2192 Enhanced _classes() extraction\n6. development-guide.md \u2192 New generator (setup/patterns/conventions)\n7. api-contracts.md \u2192 New generator (conditional, API detection needed)\n8. data-models.md \u2192 New generator (conditional, from classes with data focus)\n\nShard file naming convention:\n- Pattern: `{output_dir}/{shard-name}.md`\n- Master index: `{output_dir}/index.md`\n- Core shards: lowercase with hyphens (project-overview.md, architecture.md)\n- Conditional shards: Same pattern, only generated when relevant content detected\n-